## Setting The $LFS Variable
- add $LFS
```
root@debian:/home/crow# export LFS=/mnt/lfs
root@debian:/home/crow# echo $LFS
/mnt/lfs
```
- from root and user add to ~/.bashrc
```
echo 'export LFS=/mnt/lfs' >> ~/.bashrc
```
- add to .profile and /home/USER/.profile
```
# set LFS
export LFS=/mnt/lfs
```